    <item>
      <title>加拿大财政部长勒布朗表示不会竞选自由党领袖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/canada-finance-minister-leblanc-says-he-won-t-run-for-liberal-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大财政部长多米尼克·勒布朗 (Dominic LeBlanc) 决定不竞选自由党领袖，称他需要专注于应对唐纳德·特朗普政府的关税威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/canada-finance-minister-leblanc-says-he-won-t-run-for-liberal-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 15:25:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉政治犯遭拒，Petro 将缺席马杜罗就职典礼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/petro-to-skip-maduro-inauguration-over-venezuela-political-prisoners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚领导人表示，由于镇压不断升级以及委内瑞拉政治领导人被捕，他将缺席本周尼古拉斯·马杜罗的总统就职典礼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/petro-to-skip-maduro-inauguration-over-venezuela-political-prisoners</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 15:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部请求法院允许特朗普特别检察官报告公开</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/doj-asks-court-to-let-trump-special-counsel-report-be-released</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部请求联邦上诉法院驳回当选总统唐纳德·特朗普及其同事阻止特别顾问杰克·史密斯的最终报告公开发布的企图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/doj-asks-court-to-let-trump-special-counsel-report-be-released</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 15:02:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约州州长劳勒称提高盐含量上限对纳税人来说“至关重要”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/new-york-s-lawler-says-higher-salt-cap-critical-for-taxpayers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议员迈克·劳勒严厉批评其家乡纽约州的财政支出过高，并表示将敦促当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提高州和地方税收减免的上限，因为这会损害该州众多纳税人的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/new-york-s-lawler-says-higher-salt-cap-critical-for-taxpayers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 14:54:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普请求最高法院停止对他的封口费判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-asks-supreme-court-to-halt-jan-10-hush-money-sentencing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普请求美国最高法院介入其封口费刑事案件，以阻止其 1 月 10 日的宣判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-asks-supreme-court-to-halt-jan-10-hush-money-sentencing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:18:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 发布 eBay 广告修复程序以遵守欧盟反垄断命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/meta-floats-ebay-ads-solution-to-comply-with-eu-antitrust-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 提出在 Facebook Marketplace 上发布分类广告竞争对手 eBay Inc. 的列表，以遵守具有里程碑意义的欧盟反垄断命令，该命令还附带 7.98 亿欧元（8.22 亿美元）的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/meta-floats-ebay-ads-solution-to-comply-with-eu-antitrust-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 12:39:56 GMT</pubDate>
